content.title: Master Environment Variables in n8n with Docker!
content.description:
Learn how to efficiently set up and manage environment variables in your n8n installation using Docker. 🐳 In this video, Amjid Ali from Syncbricks will guide you through the process of adjusting environment settings to ensure seamless workflows. Discover how these changes can optimize performance and save you headaches, whether you're an experienced user or just starting out.

Timestamps:
0:00 - Introduction
1:30 - Importance of Environment Variables
3:00 - Setting Up Environment Variables
5:00 - Customizing for Performance
7:30 - Updating and Testing Configurations
